    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Situation TARFU has two main modes, the singleplayer mode &quot;Classic&quot; and the multiplayer versus mode &quot;Totally Royal&quot; both modes involve getting a high score however the singleplayer mode you compete with the local high score whereas in the versus mode you battle it out with a friend to steal points in an arena map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Characters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TheXMan</strong>: The well rounded guy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>M</strong>: Fast but her jump is weak</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mustache Guy</strong>: A slow runner but a high jumper</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Erik</strong>: Rounded with a boost</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lincoln</strong>: Quick with a more balanced jump compared to M</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Carl</strong>: Hefty but bouncy </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to learn a little more about each character? Then head to the &quot;Bios&quot; and read about every character in the game to get a better idea of who you're playing as and learn a little about their history!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Totally And Royally FUn!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got what it takes to get the highest score?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Keyboard and one controller is required to play 2 players</strong></p>",
